  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  description: 'This is for automatic off mirrors. You can adjust the trigger zone
    from the below box collider component. I recommend having it a little bit under
    ground to mitigate false triggers when going prone for example.


    You can
    toggle this object in settings panel to toggle automatic trigger feature on and
    off'
  url: 
  locked: 1
  type: 1
